<h1>Nyhedsgruppen dk.edb.internet.webdesign.html</h1><p>Gruppen er beregnet til diskussion af HTML-koder, praktisk anvendelse, syntax, faldgruber, browserinkompabilitetsproblemer etc. Spørgsmål vedrørende opbygning og anvendelse af stylesheets (CSS) er også ontopic i denne gruppe.</p><hr /><div class='newsbox'><img src='/site/graphics/icons/icon_reply.gif' alt=' | ' />&nbsp;<a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign_html/default.asp?mode=form&amp;ReplyID=%3Caas5eu%24a2e%241%40sunsite%2Edk%3E'>Svar på dette indlæg</a>&nbsp;<img src='/site/graphics/icons/icon_new.gif' alt=' | ' />&nbsp;<a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign_html/default.asp?mode=form'>Skriv et nyt indlæg</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src='/site/graphics/icons/icon_list.gif' alt=' | ' />&nbsp;<a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign_html/default.asp'>dk.edb.internet.webdesign.html</a></div>

<!-- FreeFind End No Index -->

<ul class='messageheaderlist'><li class='messageheaderlist'><strong class='diff'><span class='messageheader'>Afsender:</span></strong> &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href='mailto:riwen@ofir.dk'><img src='/site/graphics/icons/icon.newsgroups.mail.gif' alt='riwen@ofir.dk' /></a></li><li class='messageheaderlist'><strong class='diff'><span class='messageheader'>Organisation:</span></strong> SunSITE.dk - Supporting Opensource Software</li><li class='messageheaderlist'><strong class='diff'><span class='messageheader'>Dato:</span></strong> 2. maj 2002 kl. 21:53</li><li class='messageheaderlist'><strong class='diff'><span class='messageheader'>Emne:</span></strong> <strong>Hvordan tilg&#229;r man styles vha javascript ?</strong></li></ul>

<p><span class='normal'>Hejsa NG </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>Jeg roder lidt rundt med javascript og CSS, og kunne godt t&#230;nke mig at vide </span><br /><span class='normal'>hvordan man vha </span><br /><span class='normal'>en javascript funktion &#230;ndre styles defineret med CCS, p&#229; et &lt;span> </span><br /><span class='normal'>eksempelvis. </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>Jeg har lavet f&#248;lgende der ogs&#229; virker: </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;html> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;head> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;title> javascript &lt;/title> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;script language=&quot;Javascript&quot;> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>function starts() </span><br /><span class='normal'>{ </span><br /><span class='normal'> var color = randColor(); </span><br /><span class='normal'> document.all.content.style.color = &quot;rgb(&quot;+color+&quot;)&quot;; </span><br /><span class='normal'>} </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>function randColor() </span><br /><span class='normal'>{ </span><br /><span class='normal'> var color = Array(); </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'> for(var i = 0; i &lt;= 2; i++) </span><br /><span class='normal'> { </span><br /><span class='normal'>  color[i] = Math.floor(Math.random() * 255); </span><br /><span class='normal'> } </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'> return color[0] + &quot;,&quot; + color[1] + &quot;,&quot; + color[2]; </span><br /><span class='normal'>} </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;/script> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;/head> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;body onLoad=&quot;starts();&quot;> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;span id=&quot;content&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 40px; background-color: #efefef;&quot;> </span><br /><span class='normal'>Den kan skifte farve </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;/span> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;/body> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;/html> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>Men hvad hvis jeg vil &#230;ndre f.eks baggrundsfarven ? </span><br /><span class='normal'>Jeg har fors&#248;gt b&#229;de med </span><br /><span class='normal'>document.all.content.style.background-color = &quot;rgb(0,0,0)&quot;; </span><br /><span class='normal'>og </span><br /><span class='normal'>document.all.content.style.backgroundcolor = &quot;rgb(0,0,0)&quot;; </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>men det virker ikke ? </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>Findes der en oversigt over hvordan de forskellige styles tilg&#229;s og </span><br /><span class='normal'>eksempelvis ogs&#229; </span><br /><span class='normal'>en oversigt over de forskellige objekter/funktioner man benytter ved dHTML, </span><br /><span class='normal'>s&#229;som </span><br /><span class='normal'>getObjectById og innerHTML </span><br /><span class='normal'>De findes nemlig ikke i den javascript reference manual jeg har fundet p&#229; </span><br /><span class='normal'>tucows, eller </span><br /><span class='normal'>ogs&#229; er det blot mig der ikke kan finde dem ? </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;<a href='http://html.tucows.com/programmer/jsobjects/index.html'>http://html.tucows.com/programmer/jsobjects/index.html</a>> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>H&#229;ber I kan hj&#230;lpe, og I m&#229; futte mig hvis det er javascript gruppen jeg </span><br /><span class='normal'>h&#248;re til i, men det </span><br /><span class='normal'>er en blanding af CSS og javascript, s&#229; jeg smider det her, h&#229;ber det er ok </span><br /><span class='normal'>:) </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>m v h </span><br /><span class='normal'>Ronni </span><br /><span class='normal'><a href='http://rofe@mailme.dk'>rofe@mailme.dk</a> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'></span><br /></p><hr /><ul class='newslist'><li class='newslist'><a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign_html/default.asp?messageid=%3Caas5eu%24a2e%241%40sunsite%2Edk%3E' title='Hvordan tilg&#229;r man styles vha javascript ?'>Hvordan tilg&#229;r man styles vha javascript ?</a>&nbsp;<small class='newslist'>(02-05-02&nbsp;-&nbsp;)</small><ul class='relist'><li class='relist'><a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign_html/default.asp?messageid=%3Caas60e%24c2k%241%40sunsite%2Edk%3E' title='Re: Hvordan tilg&#229;r man styles vha javascript ...'>Re: Hvordan tilg&#229;r man styles vha javascript ...</a>&nbsp;<small class='newslist'>(02-05-02&nbsp;-&nbsp;)</small></li></ul><ul class='relist'><li class='relist'><a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign_html/default.asp?messageid=%3Caas7gi%2413a5%241%40news%2Ecybercity%2Edk%3E' title='Re: Hvordan tilg&#229;r man styles vha javascript ...'>Re: Hvordan tilg&#229;r man styles vha javascript ...</a>&nbsp;<small class='newslist'>(02-05-02&nbsp;-&nbsp;Jakob&nbsp;Andersen)</small></li></ul><ul class='relist'><li class='relist'><a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign_html/default.asp?messageid=%3Caod3dusaa0bt742iepbq31vi8tko964n95%404ax%2Ecom%3E' title='Re: Hvordan tilg&#229;r man styles vha javascript ...'>Re: Hvordan tilg&#229;r man styles vha javascript ...</a>&nbsp;<small class='newslist'>(02-05-02&nbsp;-&nbsp;find&nbsp;clausen)</small><ul class='relist'><li class='relist'><a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign_html/default.asp?messageid=%3Caasgfi%24sgk%241%40sunsite%2Edk%3E' title='Re: Hvordan tilg&#229;r man styles vha javascript ...'>Re: Hvordan tilg&#229;r man styles vha javascript ...</a>&nbsp;<small class='newslist'>(03-05-02&nbsp;-&nbsp;)</small></li></ul></li></ul></li></ul><div class='newsbox'><img src='/site/graphics/icons/icon_reply.gif' alt=' | ' />&nbsp;<a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign_html/default.asp?mode=form&amp;ReplyID=%3Caas5eu%24a2e%241%40sunsite%2Edk%3E'>Svar på dette indlæg</a>&nbsp;<img src='/site/graphics/icons/icon_new.gif' alt=' | ' />&nbsp;<a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign_html/default.asp?mode=form'>Skriv et nyt indlæg</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src='/site/graphics/icons/icon_list.gif' alt=' | ' />&nbsp;<a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign_html/default.asp'>dk.edb.internet.webdesign.html</a></div><br /><div style='text-align:center;'>Adgangen til Usenet sker gennem <a href='http://www.sunsite.dk'>SunSITE.dk</a></div><dl><dt></dt><dd></dd></dl>


